modName: Ancient eldar ceremonial and battle armor
summary: boots, gloves, 2 cuirasses, red and blue variant, craftable in ebony
descriptionHtml:
[size=6]Description[/size]
Craftable in ebony and necklace in jewellery, has same stats as ebony, can be tempered
Contains boots, gloves, cuirass (with and without visible necklace)
Does not support weight slider. Based on CBBE body, however can be equiped without problems for  any bodytype.
Called 'Ancient' armor (in list)
Contains red and blue version (in v1.10)
Added battle versions of cuirasses (in v 1.20)

[size=6]Credits
[/size]First of all, thanks to GamesWorkshop for their Warhammer40000 universe and therir eldar symbols, so the armor is fan-art of eldar armor
